high_descs: Turn left and take a step to your left then walk to the sink that's on your left and stand facing it.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of you in the sink.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk forward to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the wall in front of you then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato on the bottom shelf near the edge and close the fridge.
